Class ChooseStructurePropertyDescriptor

java.lang.Object
  java.beans.FeatureDescriptor
      java.beans.PropertyDescriptor
          de.hu.gralog.beans.propertydescriptor.ChooseStructurePropertyDescriptor

public class ChooseStructurePropertyDescriptor
extends PropertyDescriptor

This class is a special PropertyDescriptor to define properties for algorithms, structures, vertices and edges in GrALoG. This Descriptor can be used for all properties of type Structure. Use the Descriptor if you want the user to choose among all currently opened graphs in GrALog to define your property. Each Descriptor has an associated StructureTypeInfoFilter. The StructureTypeInfoFilter determines which graphs are selectable for that property ( always make sure, that the getter and setter-methods of your property have a compatible type ).

Author:
ordyniak
